{"tid":1320901,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"長輩們group收到，咩料","createTime":"2019-07-15T13:42:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T15:21:11.000Z","uid":268775,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c1f30eea852ae08343903e05e499580845daf7e2","tid":1320901,"uid":268775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:42:48.000Z","msg":"我們這個星期六20/7/2019定一個我愛香港世界日。在當曰穿上紅色丅裇或手綁紅布或 絲帶上班或去街。不須要任何單張或旗。不須要遊行、在中國, 在香港，在台灣，在世界各地的香港人或熱愛香港而出一分力。去表示我們真的熱愛香港。不用粗言穢語、不用暴力。對每一個在當天穿上紅衣的人說聲我愛香港。我們要以無聲勝有聲，以和平和愛心去寬恕曾經破壞過香港的人。用我們紅色的愛火去溶解昨天互相的不信任.將昨天的仇恨化作團結的力量。向全世界各地去表揚香港的真善美。<br />\n<br />\n請廣傳，香港人多謝你"},{"pid":"136a4204f52d8582fb2c98b5c0b6b58198535cdd","tid":1320901,"uid":35231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:44:55.000Z","msg":"唱反調, 綁黑色"},{"pid":"268a3fa98f82b879cf4ab4236db61335e0e7be82","tid":1320901,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:46:40.000Z","msg":"［建制議員應總辭］39嘆冷氣逗人工議員拎光環譴責暴力，何君堯關鍵缺席聯署<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1320529\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1320529</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9f21f724c44cf3c72886d49a19301faeda28f9c3","tid":1320901,"uid":13972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:47:18.000Z","msg":"借花敬佛<br />\n著紅色 反送中"},{"pid":"e2c64aca08372420e7b6a8de061ba496c90ce081","tid":1320901,"uid":916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:31:25.000Z","msg":"紅衛兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c0123ea0fa23c28be74979af108ce26eaa7b802","tid":1320901,"uid":276206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:21:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1FNb0Jk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1FNb0Jk.jpg&h=012ba337&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}